SYNOPSIS
     takes no arguments, and users should not launch it manually.

DESCRIPTION
     usbaudiod implements Apple's USB audio driver for devices that are
     compliant to the Audio Device Class definitions as published by the USB
     Implementers Forum. It supports enumeration, streaming and control of USB
     audio devices through the Core Audio subsystem.

